Let's start with the get function. In Java:

public static long get(long a) {
    long ret = 0;
    long now = 1;
    long t = 1;
    for (; ; ) {
        if (now * 10 > a) {
            ret += (a - now + 1) * t;
            break;
        }
        ret += now * 9 * t;
        now *= 10;
        t++;
    }
    return ret;
}

This loop calculates the total number of digits when writing all numbers from 1 to a.
